{"tid":492681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國女大膽試「穿」彩繪上健身室　熱爆互聯網","createTime":"2017-12-07T18:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T03:28:13.000Z","uid":10958,"like":84,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8362326cc0f3d91d655f45a6c9cbd0b8dcba16","tid":492681,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T18:52:22.000Z","msg":"美國女大膽試「穿」彩繪上健身室　熱爆互聯網<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/bknint-20171206222046121-1206_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fbknint-20171206222046121-1206_17011_001.html&d=W%2Bs0AQgvD%2Bcf6t2x4TcuGv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6bf2e08d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/bknint-20171206222046121-1206_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n兩名來自美國馬里蘭州巴爾的摩的30歲女子，早前與一名人體彩繪師合作，進行「仿衣」健身實驗，即兩人身上僅貼上乳貼及內褲，並畫上仿真運動衣圖案。她們前往當地一間健身室，測試旁人會否發現她們未有穿上衣服。該實驗片段於上周五（1日）放上網，已吸引逾6.5萬人觀看。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/photo/bknint-20171206222046121-1206_17011_001_01b.jpg?20171206234855\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171206222046121-1206_17011_001_01b.jpg%3F20171206234855&h=bca7e806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從片段可見，人體彩繪師塞德爾（Jen Seidel）先耐心地為賴利及盧喬蒂畫上衣服，鏡頭一轉，兩人已分別「穿上」不同顏色的運動衣，並向鏡頭展示成果；其後她們前往健身室參加課程，職員先後帶兩人到處參觀及試用多款儀器，該名職員一直未有發現她們身上的彩繪，直到兩人出言提醒，才恍然大悟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/photo/bknint-20171206222046121-1206_17011_001_02b.jpg?20171206234855\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171206222046121-1206_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20171206234855&h=e4b9412e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賴利及盧喬蒂隨後繼續健身，突然一名男子經過，並邊脫下眼鏡，邊用疑惑的語氣說：「我已經好久沒有換眼鏡，快有兩年。」又稱真的很難知道兩人是否真的有穿衣服。盧喬蒂事後笑指，人體彩繪是一個不錯的方法，以逃避洗衣的煩惱。"},{"pid":"80fbef803e2c88d325a80f5b5a973a2a2c82f850","tid":492681,"uid":10576,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T19:34:43.000Z","msg":"右邊好似幾正"},{"pid":"b2787e9dcfc92daa1590ae4c68a681780126cda2","tid":492681,"uid":82528,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盧喬蒂事後笑指，人體彩繪是一個不錯的方法，以逃避洗衣的煩惱。</blockquote><br />\n沖涼唔麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef883909b84b80489ba542d99ff630616ba287df","tid":492681,"uid":37458,"like":783,"dislike":1,"score":782,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/072117_191722aa57fac812845e65c1a06d0105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F072117_191722aa57fac812845e65c1a06d0105.jpg&h=015ff177&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25552ec8edb16e81cae383c63f9b4f86fe64655c","tid":492681,"uid":59753,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>右邊好似幾正</blockquote><br />\n兩個都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6080da4cbc4d38d15999bb67b4fc2e369956bc","tid":492681,"uid":8647,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>盧喬蒂事後笑指，人體彩繪是一個不錯的方法，以逃避洗衣的煩惱。</blockquote><br />\n沖涼唔麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢自己講完會唔會笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb24901c7a7a7cc12627161a8da126c086b15e6a","tid":492681,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T23:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901889ada6a6155361d5074239a30ffb11f24cbb","tid":492681,"uid":9699,"like":212,"dislike":1,"score":211,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>盧喬蒂事後笑指，人體彩繪是一個不錯的方法，以逃避洗衣的煩惱。</bl